# Kofaf - Fire and Forget

Python tool for calling API with these features
- Asynchronous calling
- Throttling

## Usage

```
$ kofaf [dir]
```
`dir` specified the working directory, default to ~/.kofaf

Inside working directory
- requests/
  all the executed requests move here

- responses/
  all the responses

- kofaf.yml
  configuration file

  
